<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Vibe Coding on 知行社</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/tags/vibe-coding/</link><description>Recent content in Vibe Coding on 知行社</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/tags/vibe-coding/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Vibe Coding 实战：我用 Cursor 做了一个 AI 情感僚机</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/vibe-coding-cursor-wingman/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/vibe-coding-cursor-wingman/</guid><description>不会写代码，但用 Cursor 从零搭出了 Wingman——一个帮你分析聊天氛围、生成回复的 AI 工具。这是完整的实战过程。</description></item><item><title>用AI的人，正在悄悄变笨</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/ai-making-people-dumb/</link><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/ai-making-people-dumb/</guid><description>AI帮你写代码、写报告、导航出行，效率翻倍。但有一件事没人告诉你：用久了，那块肌肉会悄悄萎缩。</description></item><item><title>AI帮你到了终点，但路上的风景只能自己看</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/helicopter-era-ai-cant-replace-experience/</link><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/helicopter-era-ai-cant-replace-experience/</guid><description>Vibe Coding时代，AI能帮你写代码、整理数据、生成方案，但判断力只能自己踩坑练出来。从儿子考试焦虑到程序员白板死磕，说的是同一件事：没走过的路，不算你走过。</description></item></channel></rss>